  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Controls all Actions of the Program and the Programflow.
    FileHandler
    This class loads and Saves logo Programs and Images
    GraphPane
    This class draws the Turtle and all other graphical elements
    Gui
    This class sets the Layout of the Gui and allows User Interaction
    GuiListener
    This class handles the Button events, so that the Control can just await a button, instead of calling a method from the Gui directed to the Controller.
    HelpPage
    Shows a Help Page.
    Interpreter
    This class interprets all parsed commands and execute the fitting method in the controller class
    Parser
    Parses a String Array and remove comments ( ;comments ) and empty lines
    Turtle
    calculates Positions, saves direction, Color and if the Turtle is Drawing.
